OL,3,CAndy Robertson to leave Liverpool at
OL,4,Cthe end of the season
OL,6,FAndy Robertson will leave Liverpool at
OL,7,Fthe end of the season when his contact
OL,8,Fexpires, the club has announced.
OL,10,FThe Scotland captain has spent nine
OL,11,Fseasons with the Reds, making 373
OL,12,Fappearances and winning two Premier
OL,13,FLeague titles, a Champions League, the
OL,14,FFA Cup, two League Cups as well as the
OL,15,FFIFA Club World Cup, UEFA Super Cup
OL,16,Fand Community Shield.
OL,18,FHowever, the 32-year-old has been
OL,19,Flimited to just 15 starts this season
OL,20,Ffollowing the arrival of Milos Kerkez.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
