OL,3,CAndy Robertson to leave Liverpool at
OL,4,Cthe end of the season
OL,6,FSpeaking on the club's website,
OL,7,FRobertson said: "It's never easy
OL,8,Fleaving a club like Liverpool, it has
OL,9,Fbeen a huge part of mine and my
OL,10,Ffamily's life for the last nine years.
OL,11,FBut for me, players move on, other
OL,12,Fpeople move on ` the thing that stays
OL,13,Fthe same is the club and obviously the
OL,14,Ffans.
OL,26,@oD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
