OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775811901
OL,3,CAndy Robertson to leave Liverpool at
OL,4,Cthe end of the season
OL,6,F"I've had an amazing nine years here.
OL,7,FLook, I think it has been well-
OL,8,Fdocumented, especially over the last
OL,9,Fyear or so, I've had opportunities to
OL,10,Fleave and I've not taken them because
OL,11,Fof how difficult it is to leave this
OL,12,Fclub. And I wouldn't change that for
OL,13,Fthe world.
OL,15,F"But I know football moves on, I know
OL,16,Fteams move on and I think now is the
OL,17,Ftime for me to move on and go wherever
OL,18,Fmy next move is and wherever my career
OL,19,Ftakes me.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775811901
OL,3,CAndy Robertson to leave Liverpool at
OL,4,Cthe end of the season
OL,6,F"I'll always look back on amazing
OL,7,Fmemories at this football club, I've
OL,8,Fput my heart and soul into the club
OL,9,Ffor nine years and I've not got many
OL,10,Fregrets. I've grown as a man and as a
OL,11,Fperson. This club will always mean the
OL,12,Fworld to me, the fans will mean the
OL,13,Fworld to me. It has been a hell of a
OL,14,Fjourney."
OL,16,FGlasgow-born Robertson joined
OL,17,FLiverpool from Hull in an #8million
OL,18,Fdeal in 2017 and quickly set a marker
OL,19,Fwhen he was named man of the match on
OL,20,Fhis debut, a 1-0 win over Crystal
OL,21,FPalace.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
