CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775811901
OL,3,CAndy Robertson to leave Liverpool at
OL,4,Cthe end of the season
OL,6,FRobertson said: "I'll let other people
OL,7,Fsay if I'm a Liverpool legend or not `
OL,8,FI think you know me well enough that I
OL,9,Fwill never accept that," Robertson
OL,10,Fadded.
OL,12,F"But from minute one I came into this
OL,13,Ffootball club, I wanted to be
OL,14,Fsuccessful. I wanted to try to bring
OL,15,Ftrophies back to this football club,
OL,16,Ftry to help put us back onto a place
OL,17,Fwhere I believe this football club
OL,18,Fbelongs.
OL,26,@nD@QOUqD@XO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
