PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775811901
OL,3,CAndy Robertson to leave Liverpool at
OL,4,Cthe end of the season
OL,6,F"I'm very proud that I've been a part
OL,7,Fof fantastic teams that have been able
OL,8,Fto do that. The club means everything
OL,9,Fto me."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@GO]
